name: dont BREAK it
description:
Do not let the cell phone fall to the floor, you will have to slide up to avoid it.  Collect coins to unlock things in the shop.  If you liked me do not hesitate to leave a comment, it is greatly appreciated <3.
No dejes que el celular se caiga al piso, tendras que deslizar para arriba para evitarlo.  Recolecta monedas para desbloquear cosas en la tienda.  Si te gusto no dudes en dejar un comentario, se agradece mucho <3.
